{"tid":2139643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜酷刑 主動加辣保釋條件","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T16:55:10.000Z","uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37de6bfdb7e6c00da8c0dc03718fbf4f540221db","tid":2139643,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"控方今指已準備好答辯，惟辯方指需要就修訂控罪後的刑罰及犯罪要素向被告提供法律意見，申請案件押後，而<span class=\"red\">控方不反對兩人以原有條件擔保</span>。<br />\n<br />\n杜官隨即向檢控官查問修訂後的控罪最高刑則，在得悉為監禁三年後，稱原本控罪一般監禁5天至2年，然後審閱控方提供的罪案詳情，口中念念有詞，繼而向辯方大律師提出，控罪比原先嚴重，要適度收緊保釋條件。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">兩被告原先分別以一萬元及五千元現金保釋，杜官隨即下令增加兩人保釋金、將兩人的宵禁時間提前至晚九朝八，並將兩人到警署報到的次數由一次增加至四次，杜官並明言「法庭揀，唔係你揀」，拒絕遷就兩人的視像授課時間。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/O7LE27XVZ73FTZ4G6VOZ4MJYBQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FO7LE27XVZ73FTZ4G6VOZ4MJYBQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=2c48df4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FO7LE27XVZ73FTZ4G6VOZ4MJYBQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=48a52a24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/O7LE27XVZ73FTZ4G6VOZ4MJYBQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d69de0433d6df521592ec7b8686a7642a040570d","tid":2139643,"uid":57073,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"控又係你 判又係你<br />\n直接話加到50萬呀笨"},{"pid":"bed966b02cbfceb2ce8d10633486f101f699b422","tid":2139643,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy